data.description: Great home on over an acre in town! Don't miss out on this beautiful brick home with hardwood floors, granite counter tops, and so much character. With several bonus rooms in the house, you can have a study, play room, and more. Huge fenced in yard with beautiful Pecan trees providing shade. There is also a large carport and a shop with electricity, great for extra storage or working on projects. Buyer or buyer's agent to verify room sizes and other information contained herein.
